description: List the export jobs for the Amazon SageMaker Model Card.

parameters.name: ModelCardName
parameters.description: List export jobs for the model card with the specified name.

nested_items.name: ModelCardExportJobSummaries
nested_items.description: The summaries of the listed model card export jobs.

nested_items.name: ModelCardExportJobName
nested_items.description: The name of the model card export job.

nested_items.name: ModelCardExportJobArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model card export job.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The completion status of the model card export job.

nested_items.name: ModelCardName
nested_items.description: The name of the model card that the export job exports.

nested_items.name: ModelCardVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the model card that the export job exports.

nested_items.name: CreatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the model card export job was created.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the model card export job was last modified..

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, SageMaker returns this token. To retrieve the next set of model card export jobs, use it in the subsequent request.
